Dragon Fruit Berliner Weisse with Glitter

![Halloween Beer](https://photos.tylercipriani.com/thumbs/35/cb6e3fb84522b207d7738556127e06/large.jpg)

I figured I should post about my Halloween beer before it's Thanksgiving. This
beer took 3rd place in the Prairie Homebrewing Companions [Hoppy
Halloween](http://www.hoppyhalloween.com/results.htm) competition in the
"Halloween theme beer" category.

> The blood of a unicorn will keep you alive, even if you are an inch from
> death, but at a terrible price. You have slain something pure and defenceless
> to save yourself, and you will have but a half-life, a cursed life, from the
> moment the blood touches your lips.
>
> -- Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Stone[^1]

The basic recipe is [Milk the Funk's Berliner
Weissbier](http://www.milkthefunk.com/wiki/Berliner_Weissbier#Milk_the_Funk_Berliner_Weissbier_Recipe)
with a handful of tricks.

